OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773850285
OL,3,CPE teacher banned over small boats post
OL,5,FA PE teacher who wrote "deploy the
OL,6,Fnavy" in response to a social media
OL,7,Fpost about "illegal migrant invaders"
OL,8,Fhas been barred from the classroom
OL,9,Fafter an official investigation.
OL,11,FSamuel Everett, who taught at Haughton
OL,12,FAcademy in Darlington, Co Durham, was
OL,13,Ffound guilty of unacceptable conduct
OL,14,Fby a panel of the Teaching Regulation
OL,15,FAgency after a hearing which ended
OL,16,Flast month.
OL,18,FThe panel looked at posts he made
OL,19,Fbetween December 2023 and February
OL,20,F2024 and found some were offensive.
OL,26,@mD@XOUnD@EO]oD@LOUoD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
