OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773850285
OL,3,CPE teacher banned over small boats post
OL,5,FHe has now been banned from teaching
OL,6,Fafter a review.
OL,8,FMr Everett, 29, posted on X under his
OL,9,Fown name and said he was a teacher,
OL,10,Fthe panel was told.
OL,12,FIn a judgment which has been published
OL,13,Fonline, it was found that he wrote
OL,14,F"Deploy the navy" in response to a
OL,15,Fpost saying "more boats filled with
OL,16,Fillegal migrant invaders are
OL,17,Fapproaching our shores every day. Only
OL,18,FBritain First would stop the boats and
OL,19,Fdeport all illegal migrants".
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@QO]wD@MOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773850285
OL,3,CPE teacher banned over small boats post
OL,5,FThe panel said that Britain First was
OL,6,F"widely known as a far right
OL,7,Forganisation".
OL,9,FIt said: "The post to which Mr Everett
OL,10,Fwas replying used the word 'invaders',
OL,11,Fwhich was relevant to the context of
OL,12,FMr Everett's reply to the effect that
OL,13,Fthe navy should be deployed.
OL,15,F"The purpose of deploying the navy, in
OL,16,Fthe context of the word 'invaders',
OL,17,Fwas offensive as it implied advocating
OL,18,Fthe use of military force against
OL,19,Funarmed people in small boats."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@MO]qD@JOUwD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773850285
OL,3,CPE teacher banned over small boats post
OL,5,FMr Everett also posted "just get rid
OL,6,Fof the lot of them, if they hate this
OL,7,Fcountry so much they should f*** off",
OL,8,Fin response to a comment which said
OL,9,F"... we have imported many more who
OL,10,Fhate the country. The only way we
OL,11,Fsurvive is through patriotism and
OL,12,Funderstanding our history".
OL,14,FAnother of his posts said: "Completely
OL,15,Fagree, if you don't respect our laws,
OL,16,Fculture and way of life you should
OL,17,Fleave, nobody is forcing you to stay.
OL,19,F"We don't go to other peoples
OL,20,Fcountries and tell them they're wrong
OL,21,Ffor how they go about things."
OL,26,@mD@XOUoD@eO]qD@AOUtD@ZO]vD@\OU{D@AOU}D@
OL,26,A^O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773850285
OL,3,CPE teacher banned over small boats post
OL,5,FMr Everett was employed by Haughton
OL,6,FAcademy, which was part of the
OL,7,FEducation Village Academy Trust, as a
OL,8,FPE teacher from 2022 until he was
OL,9,Fdismissed in June 2024, after someone
OL,10,Fraised concerns about his posts on X.
OL,12,FThe panel recommended that Mr Everett
OL,13,Fbe allowed to continue teaching, given
OL,14,Fhis remorse and a successful placement
OL,15,Fat another school.
OL,17,FHe had deleted the posts and closed
OL,18,Fhis account, the panel was told.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773850285
OL,3,CPE teacher banned over small boats post
OL,5,FBut decision-maker Marc Cavey, on
OL,6,Fbehalf of the Secretary of State for
OL,7,FEducation, ruled that Mr Everett
OL,8,Fshould be barred from teaching for
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FMr Everett may apply for the order to
OL,12,Fbe lifted after two years.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773850285
OL,3,CPE teacher banned over small boats post
OL,5,FMr Cavey found: "In this case, and
OL,6,Fwhile noting the evidence of insight
OL,7,Fand remorse found by the panel, I have
OL,8,Fplaced considerable weight on the
OL,9,Fseriousness of the misconduct that it
OL,10,Fhas found, which included a teacher
OL,11,Fengaging in offensive dialogue on a
OL,12,Fpublic social media platform thereby
OL,13,Fdemonstrating a lack of tolerance and
OL,14,Fa lack of respect for the rights and
OL,15,Fbeliefs of others.
OL,17,F"I have also placed considerable
OL,18,Fweight on the likely negative impact
OL,19,Fof this behaviour on the reputation of
OL,20,Fthe profession.
OL,26,@mD@QOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773850285
OL,3,CPE teacher banned over small boats post
OL,5,F"I have also noted the panel's
OL,6,Ffindings that Mr Everett's behaviour
OL,7,Fwas deliberate and that there was no
OL,8,Fevidence that he was acting under
OL,9,Fduress.
OL,11,F"In my judgment the panel has, in
OL,12,Fmaking its recommendation that a
OL,13,Fprohibition order should not be
OL,14,Fimposed, failed to give sufficient
OL,15,Fweight to these factors."
OL,26,@mD@AOUsD@AOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
